<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">-</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 如果逗号也省略掉则表示重复固定的次数。</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">-</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> `[0-9]{</span><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">3}</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379">`</span><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF"> 匹配3位数字</span></span>
<span class="line"></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">"[0-9]{3}"</span><span style="--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF"> =</span><span style="--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">></span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> The</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> number</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> was</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 9.`</span><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">999</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379">`</span><span style="--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">7</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> but</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> we</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> rounded</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> it</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> off</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> to</span><span style="--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> 10.0.</span></span></code></pre>
